    (iii)
    <br>
    <strong><i>2 1 0 – powers</strong></i>
    <br>
    2 3 1<sub>4</sub>
    <br>
    = 2 x 4<sup>2</sup> + 3 x 4<sup>1</sup> + 1 x 4<sup>0</sup>
    <br>
    = 2 x 16 + 3 x 4 + 1 x 1
    <br>
    = 32 + 12 + 1
    <br>
    = 45
    <br>
    2 3 1<sub>4</sub> => <strong>45 or 45<sub>10</sub></strong>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
    (iv)
    <br>
    <strong><i>1 0 – powers </strong></i>
    <br>
    3 1<sub>8</sub>
